{"tid":1578871,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我是和理非，我接受私了 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:37:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d3699805be1a4f561001e36c1c52fb59759820e8","tid":1578871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190918/20769963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20769963&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=0e00bdaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F20769963&h=7b3d412c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190918/20769963</a><br />\n<br />\n我是和理非，我接受私了 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190918/large/1568702554_d6e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568702554_d6e9.jpg&h=9330fd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋對高牆的戰爭進入第一百天，出現了私了現象。9.15當黑社會向示威者發動襲擊時，示威者有了默契，群起還手，看到打人的黑社會分子被打倒在地，我這個和理非竟然大喊一聲：「好療癒！」大約是物以類聚的緣故，我的朋友圈中，幾乎清一色是反應跟我一樣的人。<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前，如果有人問我，在街頭遇襲應該怎麼做，我會說報警。可是短短三個月時間，香港由法治社會變成警察城市，巿民的人身安全不再受保障。由元朗恐襲開始，警黑一家的印象深深地刻在我們腦海，中秋節翌日，大批黑社會分子在淘大花園商場向巿民施襲，警察來到，卻毫無懸念地捕捉受害的年青人及途經的街坊，對施襲者網開一面。9.15依然，大批福建幫出動，無差別襲擊示威者及途人，當晚被襲擊的記者多達14人，警察來到，用盾牌遮黑幫的臉，護送黑幫離開。所以當示威者不再被動地忍受襲擊，奮起反抗時，連和理非都忍不住要開香檳。香港已非法治社會，本該維持社會秩序的警察帶頭犯法、失序，並永遠失去巿民的信任。被侵犯的人，為了保護自己、保護同路人，用私了的方式對付施襲者，不合法，卻完全合情理。是制度暴力，逼迫守法的良民用暴力方式反抗暴政。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，警察及示威者的暴力均有升級，但最近民調卻顯示不認同示威者使用過份武力的比例上升了1.8%，而「私了」也沒有令和理非割席。柒婆，是時候面對現實了。暴力鎮壓無法達成你想要的平靜。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n無可疑才最可疑 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n新城市江湖兒女 (邁克)"},{"pid":"f4f01608f5d397dee07e73e61d24cd2b319bcc6e","tid":1578871,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7b4b97934faa239caee1caab2361865fd65875b","tid":1578871,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05e8251ef432380724ae43ec77cba13a51024e6c","tid":1578871,"uid":48667,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔先係接受程度最低個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867c8818a57ceef5a03df668d61f2d083f895365","tid":1578871,"uid":101051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"和勇密不可分<br />\n兩方缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2f87bfc23ed6d17cd9e6520439f7ac3b05a805","tid":1578871,"uid":156679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"個啲叫自我防衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29677d418d02923ac9a896da4462e09f17becbaa","tid":1578871,"uid":101051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"沒有誰比誰更重要<br />\n和理非  勇武派<br />\n所有人都係香港英雄"},{"pid":"b0fa79beec50fb02f6e4e4df2b38096fe20600a9","tid":1578871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"867c8818a57ceef5a03df668d61f2d083f895365","tid":1578871,"uid":101051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"和勇密不可分<br />\n兩方缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d509ee0b988962868a97f24c17cddab8723c585f","tid":1578871,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250f974604c2234d3d87e25d70192686339f7212","tid":1578871,"uid":19821,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05e8251ef432380724ae43ec77cba13a51024e6c","tid":1578871,"uid":48667,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔先係接受程度最低個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:16:40.000Z","msg":"又唔好咁講 連登仔都係驚同温層效應姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n某程度上 以前比人鬧無乜同情心反社會既連登仔係呢場運動都進化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24106650000818f158b0daa52d0a346c40bbc88e","tid":1578871,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"64個陣 和理非當道<br />\n今時今日香港勇武派行頭！"},{"pid":"fee9107fd05f3f039223e5a9af54891904bbea64","tid":1578871,"uid":191588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"係自衛，不是私了"},{"pid":"8ba42eb26f5d54388813f7183cd392940f41dee8","tid":1578871,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29677d418d02923ac9a896da4462e09f17becbaa","tid":1578871,"uid":101051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"沒有誰比誰更重要<br />\n和理非  勇武派<br />\n所有人都係香港英雄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"只要有<span style=\"color: violet;\">盡力</span>做的話"},{"pid":"2c4a29f746bb3708247ed4552f57c67ba3b99b8c","tid":1578871,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"試吓講替天行道<br />\n唔好講私了"},{"pid":"75bbfe406b97c089cdef9a1d3aa7873cdb6d8a6c","tid":1578871,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:21:20.0